                                    <td>
                                        <img src = "../../res/img/masthead_ceefirst_small.gif" class="block" style="margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;" title="The Concise Encyclopedia of Economics" alt="The Concise Encyclopedia of Economics"/>
                                        <h1 class="title">
Capital Gains Taxes</h1>
                                        <div class="author-label">by Joseph J. Cordes</div>
                                        <a href="#abouttheauthor">About the Author</a>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                        <div style="float:right;margin-top:5px;padding-right:8px;">
